<br>
In priority to kill:<br>
Glare Lords (AE dispell) [if more than 3 during break in we evac]<br>
Tentacle Tormentors (AE dispell) [same]<br>
Amygdalan Knights (do not mez but second assist on it or root, hard to mez and got HT)<br>
Turmoil Toads (Fear)<br>
Scarelings (random tp)<br>
Phoboplasms (very hard to mez but not very dangerous)<br>
