 <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>      7 - puller methods</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
You will need magic ressistance and jboots, monk are the best puller in PoF.<br>
One think very important: we'll not have a lot of good mezzer (I mean enchant 56+) so all the pull will be 2 maximum.<br>
If your FD failed do not train the camp, take your /loc and wait to die.<br>
